sequenceDiagram
    actor User

    participant Database
    User ->>+ WebUI: 1. Delete a review
    WebUI-->>-User: 2. Confirm deletion
    alt User confirms deletion [Main flow]
        User->>+ WebUI: 3. Confirm deletion
        WebUI ->>+ Server: 4. DELETE / delete-review{review id}
        Server->>+Database: 5. Delete review
        alt Can delete
            Database-->>Server: 6. Return updated review list
            Server-->>WebUI: 7. 200 / {meta, review list}
            WebUI-->>User: 8. Display successful message
        else Can not delete [Exception flow]
            Database-->>-Server: 6. Return database error
            Server-->>-WebUI: 7. 403 / {message}
            WebUI-->>-User: 8. Display error message
        end
        
    else User cancels deletion [Exception flow]
        User->>+WebUI: 3. Cancel deletion
        WebUI-->>User: 4. Cancellation confirmed
    end
